---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Privacy policy | StartMonday.AI">
  <section class="container-content py-16 max-w-3xl">
    <span class="eyebrow">Legal</span>
    <h1 class="mt-4">Privacy policy</h1>
    <div class="prose-brand mt-10">
      <p>This policy explains how StartMonday.AI B.V. collects, uses, stores, and protects personal data under the GDPR.</p>

      <h3 class="text-ink mt-8">Data controller</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Controller: StartMonday.AI B.V.</li>
        <li>Address: Utrecht, The Netherlands</li>
        <li>Email: hello@startmonday.ai</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-ink mt-8">Data we collect</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Identity and contact data submitted via contact, sign-up, and newsletter forms.</li>
        <li>Business context data you choose to provide in messages.</li>
        <li>Technical usage data through analytics cookies when consent is given.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-ink mt-8">Purposes and legal bases</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Responding to requests and preparing proposals (contract and legitimate interest).</li>
        <li>Operating and securing the website (legitimate interest).</li>
        <li>Analytics and performance improvement (consent).</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-ink mt-8">Retention</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Lead and contact data: up to 24 months after last interaction.</li>
        <li>Operational logs: up to 12 months.</li>
        <li>Analytics data: according to vendor retention settings, anonymized where possible.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-ink mt-8">Sharing and processors</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Hosting and infrastructure providers.</li>
        <li>Email and communication tools used to respond to your request.</li>
        <li>Analytics provider (only after consent).</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-ink mt-8">Your rights</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>You may request access, correction, deletion, restriction, portability, or objection.</li>
        <li>You may withdraw consent at any time for consent-based processing.</li>
        <li>You may file a complaint with the Dutch Data Protection Authority.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-ink mt-8">Contact</h3>
      <p>Email privacy requests to <a href="mailto:hello@startmonday.ai" class="underline">hello@startmonday.ai</a>.</p>

      <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-graphite/70">Last updated: 2026-04-30</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
